    <!-- CUSTOM (Stage I2): Google Identity Services - OAuth happens entirely
         here in the HTML page, never inside the Pyodide/WASM canvas sandbox
         (confirmed no public example of OAuth working inside pygbag's WASM
         sandbox - see project memory). game/net.py only ever reads the JWT
